<title>USA: Policy Management to use Risk Data products.</title>
<headline>Policy Management to use Risk Data products.</headline>
<dateline>COLUMBIA, S.C. 1996-09-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>Policy Management Systems Corp said on Wednesday it has formed an agreement with Risk Data Corp to offer its customers Risk Data's workers compensation loss reserving and benchmarking systems.</p>
<p>Risk Data's Micro Insurance Reserve Analysis product would let Policy Management clients accurately estimate workers' compensation loss reserves, the companies said in a statement.</p>
<p>Insurance companies need to set consistent loss reserve levels, they said.</p>
